original: Kanold, Edward Lev^is, disponent, Göteborg, f. 7/2/04 i Gbg av dir. Fred K. o. Emma Keeney. G. 35 m. Anna-Greta Wickstedt. Barn: Maud f. 36, Hans 37. — Stud. o. prakt, i Tyskl. 24, Engl. 27, USA 30. Medarb. i Bröd. Kanold A-B i Gbg sed. 21, fabr:leda-re där 27-33, disp. sed. 33. Led. av styr. f. Bröd. Kanold A-B, A-B Vax-papper & Lito, Fastigh. A-B Orion, A-B Fabo, A-B Röda Sten, Byggn:-fören. Mariaplan 2 o. 3 samt Biograf A-B Fyren.
translated: Kanold, Edward Lev^is, manager, Gothenburg, b. 7/2/04 in Gothenburg to director Fred K. and Emma Keeney. M. 35 to Anna-Greta Wickstedt. Children: Maud b. 36, Hans b. 37. - Studied and worked in Germany 1924, England 1927, USA 1930. Collaborator in Bröd. Kanold A-B in Gothenburg since 1921, factory manager there 1927-1933, manager since 1933. Member of the board of Bröd. Kanold A-B, A-B Wax-paper & Lito, Real Estate A-B Orion, A-B Fabo, A-B Röda Sten, Building Association Mariaplan 2 and 3, as well as Biograf A-B Fyren.
